## Tier 1: MUST HAVE (The Core 5)

| Data Point | Source | Why It Matters | Threshold |
|------------|--------|----------------|-----------|
| **float_shares** | ratios | Low float = explosive moves | < 30M (ideal < 15M) |
| **pre_market_volume** | bars | Proves interest is real | > 500K |
| **gap_percent** | bars | Momentum already started | > 10% |
| **borrow_fee_rate** | short_data | Shorts trapped = squeeze fuel | > 20% |
| **short_ratio** | ratios | Days to cover (can't exit fast) | > 3 days |

**These 5 alone will catch 80% of runners.**

