| **short_interest** | ratios | % of float shorted | > 15% |
| **borrow_difficulty** | short_data | Hard/Very Hard = squeeze | HARD+ |
| **market_cap** | fundamentals | Small cap moves more | < $500M |
| **sentiment_score** | Finnhub (optional) | Retail piling in | > 0.5 |

