## Tier 3: IGNORE FOR RUNNERS

All of these are noise for momentum plays:
- P/E ratio, EPS, revenue growth (fundamentals don't matter for day trades)
- ROE, ROA, profit margins (irrelevant)
- Debt ratios, liquidity ratios (irrelevant)
- Dividend yield (lol)
- Analyst recommendations (lagging)

